### Upload JPG → PDF
POST http://localhost:8000/convert/jpg-to-pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ../fixtures/sample.jpg
--boundary--

### Poll task status (replace TASK_ID)
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}

### Download result (replace TASK_ID)
GET http://localhost:8000/tasks/{{task_id}}/download
